de/storyteller/.artifacts/chat-foundation-after-mobile.png)\\n\\nThe required reviewer summary was written last to [25-chat-window-foundation.summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/prompts/25-chat-window-foundation.summary.md).\"}}\nprompts/25-chat-window-foundation.codex.jsonlines:206:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_27\",\"type\":\"todo_list\",\"items\":[{\"text\":\"Inspect current workspace shell, runtime state, and visual QA workflow to identify the clean integration point for the chat pane foundation\",\"completed\":true},{\"text\":\"Implement typed session chat state and reusable chat pane components, then wire them into the workspace page with local submit behavior and role-specific rendering\",\"completed\":false},{\"text\":\"Add or update automated tests covering chat message rendering, composer behavior, and workspace integration\",\"completed\":false},{\"text\":\"Run frontend verification including lint, tests, build, git checkpoint commit, and screenshot-based visual QA through the compose app\",\"completed\":false},{\"text\":\"Write the required reviewer-facing markdown summary file as the final action\",\"completed\":false}]}}\nfrontend/src/features/session/SessionStageEditorPreview.tsx:116:            description=\"When chat asks for more options, regenerated cards can land here without collapsing the layout rhythm.\"\ndocs/product-brief.md:13:- Bidirectional control: chat can suggest UI actions, and UI actions must be echoed back into chat.\ndocs/product-brief.md:24:4. Story pitches generated by Gemini, with selection, refinement, or regeneration.\ndocs/product-brief.md:43:- Left pane is the chat workspace, about one-third width.\ndocs/product-brief.md:48:- User chat can propose structured actions such as selecting a tone or refining beats.\ndocs/product-brief.md:50:- Direct UI actions must create compact chat-visible summaries for auditability and replay.\ndocs/product-brief.md:56:- The system should periodically summarize wha