{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I have enough context to commit to an implementation shape. Plan: 1. Add backend intent models plus an auditable parser result contract that wraps the existing `ChatToUIActionBatch`, assistant reply text, and clarification/failure metada...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_34", "text": "I have enough context to commit to an implementation shape.\n\nPlan:\n1. Add backend intent models plus an auditable parser result contract that wraps the existing `ChatToUIActionBatch`, assistant reply text, and clarification/failure metadata.\n2. Introduce a Gemini-backed intent parser adapter and prompt builder under a new backend AI layer, with a deterministic fake adapter path for tests.\n3. Add a session-scoped intent parsing service and `POST /api/v1/sessions/{session_id}/chat/intents` endpoint that logs the user message and structured parser result into the event log.\n4. Expand tests for prompt assembly, parser normalization/fallback behavior, event logging, and the new API endpoint.\n5. Run targeted backend tests, linting, and any broader checks that still make sense after the targeted suite passes.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 71, "prompt_index": 32, "prompt_name": "31 \u2014 Gemini-Powered Intent Parser Service", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T04:41:16-07:00"}
