{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I\u2019ve settled on the implementation boundary: a new backend AI adapter plus a session-scoped orchestration service, not frontend wiring yet. I\u2019m editing the models, audit events, and prompt/adapter layer first so the API route can sit on...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_54", "text": "I\u2019ve settled on the implementation boundary: a new backend AI adapter plus a session-scoped orchestration service, not frontend wiring yet. I\u2019m editing the models, audit events, and prompt/adapter layer first so the API route can sit on top of stable contracts instead of the other way around.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 109, "prompt_index": 32, "prompt_name": "31 \u2014 Gemini-Powered Intent Parser Service", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T04:45:29-07:00"}
